# ===========================================
# WHAT SHOULD BE COMMITED
# ===========================================

# These files SHOULD be committed:
#
# ✅ scripts/base_watcher.py
# ✅ scripts/filesystem_watcher.py
# ✅ scripts/orchestrator.py
# ✅ scripts/SKILL.md
# ✅ scripts/requirements.txt
# ✅ Dashboard.md (template)
# ✅ Company_Handbook.md
# ✅ Business_Goals.md
# ✅ README.md
# ✅ .env.example
# ✅ .gitignore
#
# These files should NOT be committed:
#
# ❌ .env (with actual secrets)
# ❌ Logs/*.json (daily logs)
# ❌ Needs_Action/*.md (active tasks)
# ❌ Done/*.md (completed tasks - archive separately)
# ❌ Any credential files
# ❌ Any state files

# ===========================================
# EXCEPTIONS (things to explicitly include)
# ===========================================

# Keep .gitkeep files to preserve folder structure
!.gitkeep
!*/.gitkeep

# Keep example files
!.env.example
!*.example
